    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>圣经 拼图</strong> 是一款适合各个年龄段的教育和放松的游戏，从儿童到成人都可以享受。该游戏被设计为家庭休闲的绝佳选择，提供从4块开始的难度级别，让最年轻的玩家也能在拼装圣经场景时获得乐趣和学习。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏开始时，玩家将被邀请选择一幅圣经图片进行拼装。每幅图片都代表着《圣经》中的一个重要章节，完成拼图后会播放简短的剪辑，讲述图片背后的故事，提供教育性和提升心灵的体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事叙述：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个拼图包都有视频故事，告诉你图片的背景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/4a4ed5284d105992b76fccac819f7bc8.poster.avif?t=1771516398\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/4a4ed5284d105992b76fccac819f7bc8.webm?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/4a4ed5284d105992b76fccac819f7bc8.mp4?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >点击 &amp; 交换：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击一个拼图块，然后点击另一个来交换它们的位置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/47c92e48d9b0bfe7ec4b8095ee6d8b70.poster.avif?t=1771516398\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/47c92e48d9b0bfe7ec4b8095ee6d8b70.webm?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/47c92e48d9b0bfe7ec4b8095ee6d8b70.mp4?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >拖拽 &amp; 放下：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需拖动一个拼图块，就可以和其他任何拼图块交换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/987eb0c0d67e027d466ad47379558834.poster.avif?t=1771516398\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/987eb0c0d67e027d466ad47379558834.webm?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/987eb0c0d67e027d466ad47379558834.mp4?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成就： </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成特定挑战解锁成就，增强参与感和乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/5d75752787d50e0dbf3302b51a9ecfff.poster.avif?t=1771516398\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/5d75752787d50e0dbf3302b51a9ecfff.webm?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175310/extras/5d75752787d50e0dbf3302b51a9ecfff.mp4?t=1771516398\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种难度级别：</strong> 为自己或您的孩子选择理想的挑战级别，选项从4块到更多，适应玩家的技能水平。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全球和好友排行榜：</strong> 与来自世界各地的朋友和玩家进行健康竞争。每张图片都有自己的排行榜，鼓励重复玩和改进。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>启发灵感的背景音乐：</strong> 享受灵感来自《圣经》诗歌书卷的旋律，如《约伯记》、《诗篇》、《箴言》、《传道书》和《雅歌》，在游戏过程中营造宁静和沉思的氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定期内容更新：</strong> 新的额外内容将定期作为DLC发布，提供新的图片和圣经故事供您探索和拼装。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>教育体验：</strong> 除了乐趣之外，游戏还提供了学习圣经故事的机会，使屏幕时间更有意义。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>圣经 拼图</strong> 不仅仅是一个游戏；它是一个有趣且有教育意义的方式，让家庭一起探索《圣经》，确保您和您的孩子都能参与到安全且充实的活动中。立即下载，开始拼装这些美丽的圣经故事吧！</p>",
